01:23.117 --> 01:25.584
- Yeah, exactly, it's the three
to seven days before Christmas

01:25.619 --> 01:27.953
when everyone leaves to go
celebrate someplace human.

01:27.988 --> 01:30.122
- What?
LA Christmas is the best.

01:30.157 --> 01:32.791
Everyone's all bundled up
in light sweaters

01:32.827 --> 01:35.594
sitting on sexy Santa's lap
at the Beverly Center.

01:35.629 --> 01:37.362
- No, thank you.

01:37.398 --> 01:39.298
Hey, if my flight's at 4:00,
when should I leave for LAX?

01:39.333 --> 01:40.499
- Do you have TSA PreCheck?

01:40.534 --> 01:42.534
Oh, honey,
you're gonna die here.

01:42.570 --> 01:44.369
