- Why are you all still here?

02:12.700 --> 02:14.199
- Have we been released?

02:14.235 --> 02:15.767
- No, what's the Mayor
waiting for?

02:15.803 --> 02:18.203
- Oh, dear God,
this is a disaster.

02:18.239 --> 02:19.705
- What?

02:19.740 --> 02:22.841
