There's a woman
watching us right now

14:52.058 --> 14:53.825
for that building behind us.

14:53.860 --> 14:56.261
That woman thinks everything
you did today was romantic

14:56.296 --> 14:59.731
because she's been brainwashed
by some British people.

14:59.766 --> 15:02.100
What you did today is
not romantic, it's weird.

15:02.135 --> 15:05.603
And "Love Actually" sounds like
a deeply problematic movie.

15:05.639 --> 15:07.405
