the dollhouse when you said

16:02.662 --> 16:04.462
I couldn't touch it
because it was an antique

16:04.497 --> 16:06.331
that had belonged
to French royalty.

16:06.366 --> 16:07.966
- Because it did.
And you shouldn't.

16:08.001 --> 16:10.668
- You're super generous,
but Christmas makes you weird.

16:10.704 --> 16:13.171
Just let all these people
go home.

16:13.206 --> 16:17.875
- The queen of diamonds
is in your mouth, sir.

16:20.714 --> 16:23.047
- Oh, hey.
All right, there Taryn.

16:23.083 --> 16:26.617
Thank you so much.
That'll be enough.

16:26.653 --> 16:30.488
All right, everybody,
go on home.

16:30.523 --> 16:32.991
[cheers and applause]

16:33.026 --> 16:36.527
